              {
                "ol": [
                  {
                    "text" : "Flow is a form of meditation in action – a state where we are fully immersed in whatever we’re doing, losing track of time and place - In this module we are going to consider the 3 main conditions for flow.",
                    "style": "textOrderedList"
                  },
                  {
                    "text" : "Condition 1 - Flow is achieved when we are engaged in activities that are neither too difficult nor too easy. To understand our flow activities we must identify when we are bored and anxious.",
                    "style": "textOrderedList"
                  },
                  {
                    "text" : "Condition 2 - create the correct environmental conditions.",
                    "style": "textOrderedList"
                  },
                  {
                    "text" : "Condition 3 - having a clear goal.",
                    "style": "textOrderedList"
                  },
                  {
                    "text" : "Benefits of flow - There are many benefits to flow, as it allows us to perform at our best. We’re motivated, engaged, creative, and our self-esteem increases.",
